爱莎贝儿-148CM-L 粉肤 RAD054 莓谷恋Ichigotani Koi-弄脏衬衫的特别服务 2026.01.25
她颤抖着擦拭客人胸口的咖啡渍，布料下肌肤的温热让她指尖发烫。
为赔偿弄脏的西装，她带客人去员工更衣室借用衬衫。转身时却被虚掩的门挡住去路——他的手臂正撑在她耳侧。
客人在耳边低笑：“这就是…心跳服务吗？”她听见自己心跳如雷。

Elsa Babe-148CM-L Pink RAD054 Ichigotani Koi-Special Service for a Stained Shirt 2026.01.25
She trembled as she wiped the coffee stain from the customer's chest, the warmth of his skin beneath the fabric made her fingertips burn.
To compensate for the stained suit, she led the customer to the staff changing room to borrow a shirt. Turning around, she was blocked by a half-open door—his arm was propped against her ear.
The customer chuckled in her ear: "Is this… the Heartbeat Service?" She could hear her heart pounding.
Body type: 148CM-L with Pink skin tone
